<br>
THe problem is, no matter what weapons you use, you will not be able to sustain enough DPS to keep agro in either case. DPS is not very effective at instantly grabbing agro, well warrior DPS at least; only maintaining (which is why 2-handers make for good tanking weapons once you have agro established). To grab agro instantly, you will need lower delay weapons and especially proc weapons.<br>
<br>
If I were you, I would consider option for either the snowchipper/frosty combo. The Frost/Spine combo will draw the most agro; however I would not recommend using wrapped entory spine in a group because of the problems the proc causes in a group (if oyu ever have to move around, you don't want to have a running mob). A frosty/snowchipper combo will serve you just fine. you could use the snare whip/spine as an effective soloing combo because you could fear kite; but this would rely too much on weapon procs; not a good idea.<br>
